All Implemented Interfaces:
Cloneable, Data, Element, Identifiable, MapData, Spatial
public class NorthArrowElement
extends BaseElement

This class provides functions for drawing a north arrow element. When a NorthArrowElement is added to an element container programmatically (that is, not through container's UI such as layout tool in PageLayout), an associated Map object must be set, otherwise it can't be serialized.
